OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney describes how songs
OL,4,Ccan unite people on political spectrum
OL,6,FSir Paul McCartney has described how
OL,7,F"valuable" it is that songs such as
OL,8,FThe Beatles' Hey Jude can unite people
OL,9,Fat different ends of the political
OL,10,Fspectrum.
OL,12,FSpeaking on The Rest Is Entertainment
OL,13,Fpodcast, he also told hosts Richard
OL,14,FOsman and Marina Hyde that he refuses
OL,15,Fto pose for photos with fans because
OL,16,Fhe does not want to feel "like that
OL,17,Fmonkey".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@JO]xD@ZOUyD@GO]
