CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778785872
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney describes how songs
OL,4,Ccan unite people on political spectrum
OL,6,FReferring to the 1968 song, which he
OL,7,Fwrote for the band, Sir Paul, 83,
OL,8,Fsaid: "You do something like Hey Jude
OL,9,Fand you see the whole audience singing
OL,10,Ftogether.
OL,12,F"In Trump's America, where Republicans
OL,13,Fand Democrats are at each other's
OL,14,Fthroats ` when we do that song,
OL,15,Fthey're not.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778785872
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney describes how songs
OL,4,Ccan unite people on political spectrum
OL,6,F"They're all loving it. And it's like,
OL,7,F'wow'. Suddenly this room has
OL,8,Fforgotten all of that. We're not going
OL,9,Fto argue; we're just going to sing
OL,10,Ftogether. Those kinds of things, I
OL,11,Fthink, are valuable."
OL,13,FSir Paul said he realised it is a
OL,14,F"radical" decision to not pose for
OL,15,Fphotos with his fans.
OL,17,FHe explained: "Down on the south coast
OL,18,Fof France in Saint Tropez, there's a
OL,19,Fman on the beachfront who has a
OL,20,Fmonkey, and you pay to have your photo
OL,21,Ftaken with the monkey.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]vD@AOUvD@IO]yD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
