PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778785872
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney describes how songs
OL,4,Ccan unite people on political spectrum
OL,6,F"I really do not want to feel like
OL,7,Fthat monkey. And when I take a picture
OL,8,Fwith someone, I do feel like him. I'm
OL,9,Fnot me anymore ` I'm suddenly
OL,10,Fsomething else."
OL,12,FSir Paul, who is due to release his
OL,13,Flatest solo album on May 29, said he
OL,14,Fis often asked how he has stayed so
OL,15,F"normal" despite his huge success
OL,16,Fspanning seven decades.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]wD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
