CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778785872
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney describes how songs
OL,4,Ccan unite people on political spectrum
OL,6,FHe told the podcast: "I think the
OL,7,Ftruth is my family. I was very lucky `
OL,8,FI came from a very loving family of
OL,9,Fvery smart working-class people. And I
OL,10,Falways say to people: don't
OL,11,Funderestimate the working-class."
OL,13,FThe Rest Is Entertainment podcast can
OL,14,Fbe listened to from Thursday, while
OL,15,FSir Paul was also interviewed for The
OL,16,FRest Is History podcast with historian
OL,17,FTom Holland, which is available from
OL,18,FFriday.
OL,26,@nD@VOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
