PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778785872
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney describes how songs
OL,4,Ccan unite people on political spectrum
OL,6,FHe told Holland that he believed The
OL,7,FBeatles' sense of humour was due to
OL,8,Ftheir Liverpool upbringing.
OL,10,F"I do think the character of Liverpool
OL,11,Fis a very strong one," he said.
OL,13,F"I think with the Irish influence and
OL,14,Fthen coming through the war, and
OL,15,Fhaving to be happy when bombs were
OL,16,Ffalling, there was a lot of music when
OL,17,FI was a kid.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@VO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
